title: The Anchor
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Not many veg choices in this city, and this pub restaurant offers several vegetarian entrees that can be requested vegan like the roasted veggie philly sandwich (omit cheese and the butter), the portobello mushroom burger, and the black bean veggie burger. Some salads and pasta dishes, pizza.
